author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
"Caramel" is the latest single by Sleep Token and I loved it. However, you wouldn't know that I appreciated the whole track in this review because much of it had to be cut to get past the thinking computer. So please watch the song in its entirety here:  
https://youtu.be/4iSvoQNfrrk?si=NsKNZFoC7Fr6BvhM
If you want to watch Rock Feeds' review in full,  visit: 
https://youtu.be/HXN1OHxdBEU?si=WIVSV2-kPd12RnLq

The new Darkness album "Dream On Toast" is out now: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/
